dlentry.dd:
You must grant permission for code in the external directory. Ensure that the
                        $SDC_CONF/sdc-security.policy file contains the following
                    lines:
                    // user-defined external directory
grant codebase "file://<external directory>-" {
  permission java.security.AllPermission;
};

For
                    example:// user-defined external directory
grant codebase "file:///opt/sdc-extras/-" {
  permission java.security.AllPermission;
};
